data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath located in New Construction community Longwood Crossing. Spacious 2-story layout with vaulted ceilings on first floor. Large living room with electric fireplace. Updated stainless steel appliances with granite countertops and large pantry in your kitchen. Open loft with large master suite. His/Her Walk-in closets with plenty of space for storing and shelving. Double Vanity, Garden tub and separate shower. Additional spacious rooms and guest bathroom with luxury, cultural marble. Laundry Room, 3-Car Garage. and Concrete Patio as well. Schedule your showing today to see this beautiful home!
